text: Hai dumna gata inong nyang ceudah Peurumoh Nabi sit bandum gata Inong biasa laen that leupah Meunyo bit gata taplihara droe Bek peuch‘ek-ch‘ek droe ‘oh taseumeugah Meunyo leumoh that watee tamarit Di agam keubit napsu jigagah Nyang na peunyaket dalam atejih Meunapsu di jih keu buet nyang salah Teuma tamarit lagee biasa
